He hated Father’s Day and said it was a load of rubbish cooked up to make money, I agree with him. He was a strange bloke but we got on really well once I’d grown up past my teens. 5 years ago he passed away but I know if he was here he’d be so pissed I mentioned him on Father’s Day. I kinda miss him. - I never share anything personal on social media, EVER. So this is the first and last time. Cheers! ✌️
